<plot>Four relationships spanning the four corners of the globe are put to the ultimate test when they learn the world may end in eight minutes - the duration of time it takes light to travel from the sun to the Earth. Each is finally forced to confront the most trying dynamics of their relationship in order to reconcile differences and face Earth's final moments: with love and without fear but, most importantly, together.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?336222</url></doc>
